high_descs: Turn left, move to the counter, right of the refrigerator.
Pick up the knife from the counter.
Turn left, move to the bin at the end of the island.
Cut the apple, in the bin, in to sections.
Put the knife in the bin.
Pick up a section of apple.
Turn left, move to in front of the microwave.
Put the apple section in the microwave, cook it, pick it back up.
Turn left, move to the bin at the end of the island.
Put the cooked apple section in the bin.
anns.task_desc: Place a slice of cooked apple into the trash.

high_descs: Turn, go across the room to the fridge, take a right and go to the counter to the right of the fridge.
Pick up the butter knife on the counter.
Go to the trash can at the end of the counter.
Slice the apple in the trash can.
Put the butter knife in the trash can.
Pick up an apple slice out of the trash can.
Turn around and go to the microwave.
Cook the apple slice in the microwave.
Turn and go back to the trash can.
Put the warm apple slice in the trash.
anns.task_desc: Put a hot slice of apple in the trash can.

high_descs: Walk towards the counter next to the fridge
Grab a knife from the counter
Walk with the knife towards the trash can
Slice apple in the trash can
Put knife in the trash can
Pick up an apple piece from the trash can
Walk with the apple piece towards the microwave
Put the apple piece inside the microwave, cook it and take it out
Walk with the apple piece towards the trash can
Put the apple piece inside the trash can
anns.task_desc: Slice apple in the trash can, grab a piece, cook it in the microwave, put it in the trash can
